### 1. Test Health Status (Public GET)
GET http://localhost:8080/api/test/status

###

### 2. Admin Login — copy the token from response
POST http://localhost:8080/api/auth/login
Content-Type: application/json

{
    "username": "admin",
    "password": "admin123"
}

###

### 3. ADMIN — Add stock to Hyundai Chennai (dealerId=2)
### Paste your token below after Bearer
POST http://localhost:8080/api/admin/inventory/add
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer eyJhbGciOiJIUzI1NiIsInR5cCI6IkpXVCJ9.eyJzdWIiOiJhZG1pbiIsImlhdCI6MTc3Mzk4NDQyOSwiZXhwIjoxNzc0MDcwODI5fQ.a-5UsnWpWSbO9vTN1hPdnJHNVj40xhLJyhZa2OETVf8

{
    "dealerId": 2,
    "variantId": 1,
    "colourId": 1,
    "quantity": 5
}

###

